{"tid":1298201,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"一國一制又出招！ 香港3年內引進「信用評分系統」","createTime":"2019-07-08T21:35:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T00:52:33.000Z","uid":268592,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"ddebb77e1e4d92e9e6147482c5733f72feb4bf00","tid":1298201,"uid":268592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T21:35:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2846513?fbclid=IwAR3pcghR5c3L3urYlFepAElFrKw1TROfbt5DMQ4W0zjOPNGsoSbm6r12ywA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2846513%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3pcghR5c3L3urYlFepAElFrKw1TROfbt5DMQ4W0zjOPNGsoSbm6r12ywA&d=Xf5vvBv8GY7fsWMyNBE0dgbFtlMfP7wF5OAPhGI7yCY%3D&h=651314c3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2846513%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3pcghR5c3L3urYlFepAElFrKw1TROfbt5DMQ4W0zjOPNGsoSbm6r12ywA&h=3de9c05f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2846513?fbclid=IwAR3pcghR5c3L3urYlFepAElFrKw1TROfbt5DMQ4W0zjOPNGsoSbm6r12ywA</a><br />\n有冇手足留意呢段新聞，好恐怖。要廣推，不要中共信用評分系統!<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb2f87d35fe012fcae8b15c81c63623e19a14eb5","tid":1298201,"uid":58841,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T21:35:57.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕中國自2014年開始逐步建設「社會信用系統」，並對評鑑分數未達標準的人民，施加更多的限制。根據廣東省政府本月5日頒布的《粵港澳大灣區建設3年行動計劃（2018-2020年）》，3年內擬在廣東、澳門以及香港全面性地建構「社會信用評分」等相關制度與體系。<br />\n<br />\n在同日公布的《粵港澳大灣區發展規劃綱要》中，在「重大意義」的部份載明，此建設是習近平「親自謀劃、親自部署、親自推動的重大國家戰略」，也是「推動一國兩制事業發展的新實踐」。<br />\n<br />\n該文件的第42項載明，除了將研究制定廣東省社會信用條例，以建立包括信用資訊的蒐集和共享機制、「紅黑名單」和信用聯合獎懲制度以外，也將推動與港澳之間的信用資訊共享、信用評價標準的接軌、信用產品互認、信用服務機構資質互認等合作，並探索依法對區域內企業聯動實施信用獎勵和失信懲戒等措施。<br />\n<br />\n而《粵港澳大灣區建設三年行動計劃（2018-2020年）》中的第75條則載明，「加快社會信用體系和市場監管體系建設。研究制定廣東省社會信用條例。探索依法對大灣區內企業聯動實施信用激勵和失信懲戒。建成全省統一的市場監管信息平台。」<br />\n<br />\n中國近年來推行「社會信用評分系統」監控14億人民，個人倘若信用等級過低，除了被禁止購買大眾運輸工具票券、限制出境外，也可能被限制購買保險、房產及禁止投資其他金融商品。中國「格鬥狂人」徐曉冬今年5月傳出被評為「D級」，除了被限制不得購買大眾運輸工具票券以外，徐曉冬也不能進入酒店和高爾夫球場、不准裝修、新建、擴建房屋，甚至連旅遊渡假也被禁止。"},{"pid":"22de0d23af141396c92e6d73424d6b9d32907794","tid":1298201,"uid":60434,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T21:36:12.000Z","msg":"可唔可以咪撚1條新聞出20個po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b06ea26b9e7d0f8c7013a3c5eb5c1e18e9a91e7","tid":1298201,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T21:37:09.000Z","msg":"屌你老母習維尼真係想搞帝制<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"171b9aea9a2f26b847fd4a594141aef4115345f3","tid":1298201,"uid":120715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T22:11:05.000Z","msg":"香港人最愛旅遊<br />\n到時一定更多人會上街遊行"},{"pid":"bd87caed7ed5dd31befc10d5018714fe5f1b936c","tid":1298201,"uid":261914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T22:12:32.000Z","msg":"watch dog現實版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f49cb8ab64a47b3fa7ec90d77b9ea31ef30f993","tid":1298201,"uid":246884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T22:23:16.000Z","msg":"唉屌你老母"},{"pid":"1954681263fa3da3062f3460b6a8ef9b0ba1ada2","tid":1298201,"uid":113124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T22:33:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc1c0968f1a6ebb2e2cc1ce3a03161341d050af0","tid":1298201,"uid":113124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T22:35:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd0828b5b18022e1537b68d8f4d2fa6c2433aca8","tid":1298201,"uid":140802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T23:22:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class